==Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|己}}), the month of {{ill|August|ja|8月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|White Dew|ja|白露}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|寒露}}) as applicable.

==Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu}} for {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉}} is as follows.
=== 選日 ===
The day of {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Large Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=大土}}.


