==Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|August|ja|8月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (from {{ill|White Dew|ja|白露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|寒露|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.
