'''Yin Water Rooster also known as 癸酉''' (mizu no totori, kisui no tori, kiyuu) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 10th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Jinshin|ja|壬申|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshin|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Koushoku|ja|甲戌|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koushoku|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Water|ja|水|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Rooster|ja|酉|1=Rooster (zodiac)|2=ja|3=酉|4=fr|5=Coq (astrologie chinoise)|6=nl|7=Haan (astrologie)|lt=Rooster (酉)|1=Rooster (zodiac)|lt=Rooster (酉)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rooster|13=User:Immanuelle/Rooster (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Metal|ja|金|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (金)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) (i.e. Metal generates Water).

