==Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s Years== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 13 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=癸酉|4=zh|5-癸酉|6=ko|7=계유|lt_ko=계유|8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 13|13 AD]] * [[:en:AD 73|73 AD]] * [[:en:AD 133|133 AD]] * [[:en:193|193 AD]] * [[:en:253|253 AD]] * [[:en:313|313 AD]] * [[:en:373|373 AD]] * [[:en:433|433 AD]] * [[:en:493|493 AD]] * [[:en:553|553 AD]] * [[:en:613|613 AD]] * [[:en:673|673 AD]] * [[:en:733|733 AD]] * [[:en:793|793 AD]] * [[:en:853|853 AD]] * [[:en:913|913 AD]] * [[:en:973|973 AD]] | * [[:en:1033|1033 AD]] * [[:en:1093|1093 AD]] * [[:en:1153|1153 AD]] * [[:en:1213|1213 AD]] * [[:en:1273|1273 AD]] * [[:en:1333|1333 AD]] * [[:en:1393|1393 AD]] * [[:en:1453|1453 AD]] * [[:en:1513|1513 AD]] * [[:en:1573|1573 AD]] * [[:en:1633|1633 AD]] * [[:en:1693|1693 AD]] * [[:en:1753|1753 AD]] * [[:en:1813|1813 AD]] * [[:en:1873|1873 AD]] * [[:en:1933|1933 AD]] * [[:en:1993|1993 AD]] | * {{ill|2053 AD|ja|2053年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2053|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2053 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2113 AD|ja|2113年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2113|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2113 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2173 AD|ja|2173年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2173|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2173 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2233 AD|ja|2233年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2233|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2233 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2293 AD|ja|2293年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2293|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2293 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2353 AD|ja|2353年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2353|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2353 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2413 AD|ja|2413年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2413|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2413 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2473 AD|ja|2473年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2473|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2473 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2533 AD|ja|2533年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2533|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2533 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2593 AD|ja|2593年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2593|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2593 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2653 AD|ja|2653年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2653|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2653 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2713 AD|ja|2713年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2713|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2713 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2773 AD|ja|2773年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2773|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2773 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2833 AD|ja|2833年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2833|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2833 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2893 AD|ja|2893年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2893|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2893 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2953 AD|ja|2953年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2953|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2953 AD|qq=}} |} ==Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s Months== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:August|August]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=癸酉|4=zh|5-癸酉|6=ko|7=계유|lt_ko=계유|8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Bailu (solar term)|White Dew]] until the day before [[:en:Hanlu|Lesser Cold]]) as applicable. ==Yin Water Rooster (癸酉)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=癸酉|4=zh|5-癸酉|6=ko|7=계유|lt_ko=계유|8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=}} is as follows. === 選日 === The day of {{ill|Kiyuu|ja|癸酉|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=癸酉|4=zh|5-癸酉|6=ko|7=계유|lt_ko=계유|8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=}} is the 4th day of {{ill|Large Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=大土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Large Earth|qq=}}.
